{"tid":1565170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒： 失蹤的抗爭兒童被人遺忘","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T09:10:49.000Z","uid":262529,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"91c9b837e666f8a52fcceb9e98d2fd5d868feb88","tid":1565170,"uid":262529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/disappearing-children-of-hong-kong-forgotten-in-the-protest-chaos-20190905-p52ohx.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fdisappearing-children-of-hong-kong-forgotten-in-the-protest-chaos-20190905-p52ohx.html&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4Qcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=ade3438b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/disappearing-children-of-hong-kong-forgotten-in-the-protest-chaos-20190905-p52ohx.html</a><br />\n<br />\n外媒都提醒我地仲有班手足等緊我地<br />\n好多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">15歲以下</span>既手足手都被人困左係兒童院成1-2個月 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇得保釋</span><br />\n開左學成個月都冇得返學<br />\n中秋都冇得返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好掛住唱歌 仲有好多手足等緊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4CTheF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4CTheF.png&h=ad0c3c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdHjXeG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdHjXeG.png&h=0b514db5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f647a180548d32585ffe17890be12f4c2eff64f3","tid":1565170,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n黃大仙廣場 ，摩士公園<br />\n觀塘海濱公園<br />\n油塘道遊樂場<br />\n2100 紅磡碼頭<br />\n2150 慈雲山中央球場大合唱<br />\n【港島】<br />\n維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌至西灣河海濱長廊<br />\n柴灣公園<br />\n【東涌】<br />\n東涌海濱長廊，百慕達公園<br />\n【離島】<br />\n2115 長洲東灣"},{"pid":"83ea71fd44016ce4b0435d14c3b685b5bd9b2b0e","tid":1565170,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1